&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Change &amp;amp; Enablement Lead to join our Enterprise Transformation team within the Delivery organization. This role is ideal for someone who thrives at the intersection of people, process, technology, and creativity — and is passionate about helping organizations successfully adopt new ways of working.&lt;/p&gt;
