&lt;p&gt;This is a client-facing consulting and execution role that combines strategic thinking with hands-on delivery. You’ll work closely with client stakeholders and cross-functional teams across creative, strategy, production, operations, and technology to help organizations navigate change and maximize the impact of new processes and platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
