&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver change and enablement plans, including communications, training, adoption strategies, and engagement activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support clients through people, process, and technology changes by translating complex transformation initiatives into clear, actionable plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate workshops, stakeholder discussions, and alignment sessions across cross-functional teams including creative, production, operations, strategy, and technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with program managers, product teams, strategists, and implementation partners to integrate change management activities into overall project delivery plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help clients establish scalable ways of working and operational models that improve collaboration, efficiency, and content production at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption and value realization for enterprise platforms and digital workflows, including Adobe Experience Cloud solutions such as Adobe Workfront, Adobe Experience Manager (AEM), and Adobe Firefly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support AI-enabled transformation initiatives by helping teams adopt new tools, workflows, and ways of working powered by generative AI and automation technologies&lt;/li&gt;
